## 3. 3 Flavors colony pack

### 3.1 `colony-full.natt`
```
Content:
  src/
  governance/
  governance/memory/bang/
  governance/memory/kim/
  governance/memory/Can/
  governance/memory/Kris/
  governance/memory/Thienlon/
  governance/memory/thiennho/
  governance/memory/phieu/
  governance/memory/boiboi/
  audit/reports/
Excludes: .git/, node_modules/, _deprecated/, database/ctytam/
Use case: disaster recovery, full archive
```

### 3.2 `colony-for-<persona>.natt`
```
Content:
  src/
  governance/
  governance/memory/<persona>/  ← CHỈ 1 persona
  audit/reports/
Use case: resurrect 1 persona target (ví dụ Kim resurrect sau wipe)
Privacy: persona khác memory KHÔNG leak
```

### 3.3 `colony-public.natt`
```
Content:
  src/
Excludes: governance/memory/*/ tất cả
Use case: share demo, open-source subset, SHTT filing (claims point to src only)
```

